description: This file defines the interface for a COSA (Cisco Open Service Architecture) plugin library, including exported API functions such as COSA_Init, COSA_IsObjSupported, and COSA_Unload. It contains license information, macro definitions, and function declarations, serving as a header for plugin implementation.

methods.name: COSA_Init
methods.description: Initializes the COSA plugin with the supported version and plugin info.

methods.name: COSA_IsObjSupported
methods.description: Checks if a specific object name is supported by the plugin.

methods.name: COSA_Unload
methods.description: Unloads or cleans up resources associated with the plugin.
